WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(Default) {
color: #ffffffff;
font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
font-size: 020px;
text-shadow: #000000ff -2px 0px 2px, #000000ff 0px 2px 2px, #000000ff 0px -2px 2px, #000000ff 2px 0px 2px;
background-color: #00000000;
}

c0000000
00:00:04.340 --> 00:00:05.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, then, Maiko,</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:07.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how about we walk home?</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:07.590 --> 00:00:08.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:11.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah!
- Wow!</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:12.010 --> 00:00:13.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's my big sister!</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:14.390 --> 00:00:15.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I work really hard,</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:16.020 --> 00:00:17.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>maybe I'll e able to meet her!</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:27.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:33.080 --> 00:00:34.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:35.080 --> 00:00:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, boy. Would the two of them</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:36.790 --> 00:00:38.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just hurry up
and make up already?</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:39.670 --> 00:00:42.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:42.710 --> 00:00:45.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[The Peggies' "Kimi no sei"]</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:45.630 --> 00:00:52.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000014
00:01:27.960 --> 00:01:34.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000015
00:01:54.320 --> 00:02:01.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:10.010 --> 00:02:11.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door creaks open]
- I'm home.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:11.630 --> 00:02:13.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're back late.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:13.380 --> 00:02:14.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I ended up having
to cook a meal,</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:14.970 --> 00:02:16.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>clean, and do some laundry
while I was there.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:18.930 --> 00:02:20.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is that all?</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:23.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- My take-away from today
is that I need</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:23.600 --> 00:02:24.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for you guys to make up.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:25.060 --> 00:02:26.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's how I'm really feeling
about all this.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:28.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:02:29.320 --> 00:02:31.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Time for bed.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000026
00:02:31.490 --> 00:02:33.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No reward for going over
to check on</b></Default>

c0000027
00:02:33.150 --> 00:02:34.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your little sister for you?</b></Default>

c0000028
00:02:34.280 --> 00:02:35.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have an early
morning meeting</b></Default>

c0000029
00:02:35.740 --> 00:02:36.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to prepare for the gig.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:02:37.370 --> 00:02:38.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000031
00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:41.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shower running over TV]</b></Default>

c0000032
00:02:42.290 --> 00:02:44.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [humming]</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:44.870 --> 00:02:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
Oh, no. The window's open.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:02:49.710 --> 00:02:50.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasping]</b></Default>

c0000035
00:02:50.750 --> 00:02:52.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasping]</b></Default>

c0000036
00:02:52.510 --> 00:02:54.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- An offer for you.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:02:54.340 --> 00:02:55.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How would you like to die?</b></Default>

c0000038
00:02:55.380 --> 00:02:56.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [screams]</b></Default>

c0000039
00:02:56.890 --> 00:02:58.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, this is not
the smile you want!</b></Default>

c0000040
00:02:58.850 --> 00:03:00.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're going
to study up on Mai,</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:00.390 --> 00:03:02.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you should have gone with
something that's more pleasant!</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:02.930 --> 00:03:05.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, what am I supposed to do?</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:05.440 --> 00:03:07.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The retake for the commercial
is already tomorrow</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:09.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I haven't gotten anywhere
with this!</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:11.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't think anything's going
to change now.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:11.650 --> 00:03:13.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- D--Don't say it so bluntly!</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:13.740 --> 00:03:15.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Isn't it okay
to not force yourself</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:15.570 --> 00:03:17.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to do things you can't do?
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:17.490 --> 00:03:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mediocrity is just fine.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:19.450 --> 00:03:21.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're being too greedy
with this.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:21.620 --> 00:03:23.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you going home?</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:23.290 --> 00:03:25.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If I get back too late,
Mai gets in a bad mood.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:26.620 --> 00:03:28.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hold on!
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:28.290 --> 00:03:30.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I--it's just...</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:30.380 --> 00:03:31.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I, uh...</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:34.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wanna take time relaxing
in the bath.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:34.210 --> 00:03:36.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So can you stay here
till I get out?</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:36.590 --> 00:03:39.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? I don't get why you'd
need me to stay here.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:39.180 --> 00:03:40.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makes no flippin' sense.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:03:40.760 --> 00:03:43.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wh--When I'm in the bath
by myself, I--</b></Default>

c0000061
00:03:43.430 --> 00:03:46.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>well, sometimes I get this
bad feeling that I hate.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:03:47.060 --> 00:03:48.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, so you're just afraid.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:03:48.730 --> 00:03:49.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't act all high and mighty!</b></Default>

c0000064
00:03:50.060 --> 00:03:51.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You jumped at that bath scene,
too!</b></Default>

c0000065
00:03:51.610 --> 00:03:53.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll do it if we
can bathe together.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:03:53.690 --> 00:03:56.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Y--you'd have
to ask my big sister about that.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:03:56.700 --> 00:03:58.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Right. Let me go get Mai on
the phone, then.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:03:58.490 --> 00:04:00.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- W--wait! Never mind.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:00.370 --> 00:04:02.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]
You're the worst!</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:02.200 --> 00:04:04.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]
- I'm home.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:07.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- W--welcome back, big brother.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:07.160 --> 00:04:08.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:08.620 --> 00:04:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Y--you got back early.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:11.170 --> 00:04:13.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is this a new game
or something?</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:13.500 --> 00:04:15.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I--if you think Kaede
just plays games all</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:15.710 --> 00:04:16.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the time, you're wrong!</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:17.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede has a lot of things</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:18.050 --> 00:04:19.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>weighing on her mind, too!</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:19.550 --> 00:04:21.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What kind of things made
you end up like that?</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:23.310 --> 00:04:25.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother, you promise
you won't laugh?</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:26.100 --> 00:04:27.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I promise.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:04:31.810 --> 00:04:33.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you think?</b></Default>

c0000083
00:04:33.570 --> 00:04:35.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
It's smells exactly</b></Default>

c0000084
00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:38.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like the closet.
- That's all you have to say?</b></Default>

c0000085
00:04:38.110 --> 00:04:40.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh. You look kinda like
a middle schooler.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:04:40.700 --> 00:04:41.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- O--of course!</b></Default>

c0000087
00:04:42.070 --> 00:04:44.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede's a bona fide
middle school student.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:04:44.450 --> 00:04:46.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And she thinks that her time
is almost here</b></Default>

c0000089
00:04:46.750 --> 00:04:49.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to start putting some
elbow grease into it.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:04:51.210 --> 00:04:52.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000091
00:04:52.420 --> 00:04:54.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Just don't push yourself
too hard.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:04:54.540 --> 00:04:56.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The problem is big brother's
been bringing home more</b></Default>

c0000093
00:04:56.880 --> 00:04:59.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>new girls than Kaede
can keep up with lately.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:04:59.340 --> 00:05:01.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because of this,
Kaede feels like she needs</b></Default>

c0000095
00:05:01.300 --> 00:05:02.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to get her act together.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:04.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, I'm back.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:04.430 --> 00:05:06.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hi. Welcome back, Nodoka.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:06.520 --> 00:05:07.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your uniform?</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:07.890 --> 00:05:09.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nice! So cute!</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:09.480 --> 00:05:11.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You really think so?</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:11.100 --> 00:05:12.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.
- [giggles]</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:12.150 --> 00:05:13.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, I brought a present.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:13.980 --> 00:05:15.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you so much!</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:15.730 --> 00:05:17.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:19.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, it's the teensy bit
fancy pudding!</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:19.860 --> 00:05:21.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's right.
I got these, too.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:21.780 --> 00:05:23.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're tickets to our show.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:05:23.780 --> 00:05:25.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give one to Nodoka for me.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:05:25.240 --> 00:05:27.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You could just give it
to her yourself.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:05:27.410 --> 00:05:29.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The other one's for you
so come and watch it together.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:32.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah. And I also sent one
to Nodoka's mom.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:05:32.790 --> 00:05:34.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000113
00:05:34.210 --> 00:05:36.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And, action!</b></Default>

c0000114
00:05:37.050 --> 00:05:38.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000115
00:05:39.050 --> 00:05:41.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

c0000116
00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:43.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That one was great!</b></Default>

c0000117
00:05:43.470 --> 00:05:44.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Awesome work today.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:05:45.050 --> 00:05:46.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you so much
for having me.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:49.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cheers and applause]</b></Default>

c0000120
00:05:49.850 --> 00:05:52.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

c0000121
00:05:53.810 --> 00:05:55.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's good that went well, huh?</b></Default>

c0000122
00:05:55.190 --> 00:05:56.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What are you talking about?</b></Default>

c0000123
00:05:56.940 --> 00:05:59.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It took me 12 takes.
That's pathetic.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:06:01.820 --> 00:06:05.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, it's impossible
for me to be like my sister.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:05.370 --> 00:06:07.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?
- I seriously can't even imagine</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:07.830 --> 00:06:10.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>living under this much pressure
every single day of my life.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:10.370 --> 00:06:12.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way.
Oh, man!</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:12.750 --> 00:06:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do I do?</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:14.580 --> 00:06:17.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You can worry about that once
you actually get that famous.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:17.340 --> 00:06:19.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's not what
I'm talking about, okay?</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:21.550 --> 00:06:22.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you wanna do, then?</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:23.340 --> 00:06:25.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To become someone more like Mai?</b></Default>

c0000133
00:06:25.470 --> 00:06:27.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm not sure anymore.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:06:27.100 --> 00:06:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think that's what I wanted in
the past.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:06:29.140 --> 00:06:30.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now?</b></Default>

c0000136
00:06:32.430 --> 00:06:33.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000137
00:06:36.440 --> 00:06:37.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Answer it.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:06:37.480 --> 00:06:38.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000139
00:06:39.570 --> 00:06:42.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello?
- Why are you answering, Sakuta?</b></Default>

c0000140
00:06:42.690 --> 00:06:44.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, well. I had something
 to tell you, so it's all right.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:06:44.950 --> 00:06:46.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Tell me?</b></Default>

c0000142
00:06:46.450 --> 00:06:48.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your dad called the home phone
a few minutes ago.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:06:48.990 --> 00:06:51.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't answer but when
the answering machine picked up,</b></Default>

c0000144
00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:54.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he'd asked if you'd meet him
two evenings from now.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:06:54.410 --> 00:06:55.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, okay. Got it.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:06:55.710 --> 00:06:57.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you for the message.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:06:57.500 --> 00:06:59.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, and the commercial shoot
ended up going really well.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:07:00.340 --> 00:07:01.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It took like 13 takes, though.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:07:01.710 --> 00:07:03.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- 12!
- Good.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:07:03.760 --> 00:07:05.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell Nodoka thanks
for taking care of it.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:07:05.630 --> 00:07:06.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:07:08.640 --> 00:07:09.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

c0000153
00:07:10.680 --> 00:07:11.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, that's right.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:07:11.930 --> 00:07:13.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai told me to give this to you.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:07:14.060 --> 00:07:16.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A ticket for that show
at the end of the month.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:07:18.520 --> 00:07:21.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know, the first time
I met my sister</b></Default>

c0000157
00:07:21.190 --> 00:07:23.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was at an audition back when I
was a kid.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:07:23.570 --> 00:07:25.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I remember it clearly.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:07:26.110 --> 00:07:28.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I was just thinking how nice
it'd be to have a little sis.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:07:28.820 --> 00:07:30.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000161
00:07:30.910 --> 00:07:32.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It made me so happy.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:07:33.660 --> 00:07:36.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, my big sister
was so awesome.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:07:36.410 --> 00:07:39.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, Mai has continued
