c0000191
00:08:48.950 --> 00:08:50.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I guess I'd say all the above.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:08:51.110 --> 00:08:52.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:08:53.070 --> 00:08:54.240 line:90% align:center
