- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000327
00:14:44.840 --> 00:14:46.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yay!
- Yeah!</b></Default>

c0000328
00:14:46.840 --> 00:14:49.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yay!
- I'm so glad.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:14:49.140 --> 00:14:50.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really did it.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:14:50.680 --> 00:14:52.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so happy for you.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:14:52.730 --> 00:14:54.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You worked so hard.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:15:01.480 --> 00:15:04.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mother was actually smiling.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:15:04.320 --> 00:15:06.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's normal for people
to smile every so often.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:15:06.740 --> 00:15:08.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not her.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:15:08.120 --> 00:15:09.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's never made
a face like that with me.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:15:11.580 --> 00:15:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That just solidifies
what I thought.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:15:13.450 --> 00:15:14.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'll always win.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:15:15.500 --> 00:15:18.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mother would rather
have my sister instead.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:15:24.260 --> 00:15:26.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't wanna go home.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000340
00:15:26.590 --> 00:15:29.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The beach sounds good.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:15:30.640 --> 00:15:31.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000342
00:15:32.390 --> 00:15:34.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.
Just for a bit.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:15:43.780 --> 00:15:44.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000344
00:15:47.030 --> 00:15:47.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey!</b></Default>

c0000345
00:15:50.320 --> 00:15:52.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000346
00:15:53.540 --> 00:15:55.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Knock it off!
- Let go!</b></Default>

c0000347
00:15:55.620 --> 00:15:57.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's clear to me that there's
no reason for me</b></Default>

c0000348
00:15:57.420 --> 00:15:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be here anymore!
- Toyohama!</b></Default>

c0000349
00:15:59.290 --> 00:16:00.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000350
00:16:01.040 --> 00:16:02.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The hell are you doing?
- I've had enough of this!</b></Default>

c0000351
00:16:02.960 --> 00:16:05.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? No way you have!
- Let go!</b></Default>

c0000352
00:16:05.170 --> 00:16:07.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let go of me, you idiot!
- Who's the idiot, now?</b></Default>

c0000353
00:16:07.300 --> 00:16:08.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This has nothing
to do with you!</b></Default>

c0000354
00:16:08.970 --> 00:16:11.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then don't use such a cruel
and unfair tactic to test me!</b></Default>

c0000355
00:16:11.550 --> 00:16:12.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only an idiot goes into</b></Default>

c0000356
00:16:12.810 --> 00:16:14.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the ocean assuming they'll
be saved!</b></Default>

c0000357
00:16:14.180 --> 00:16:15.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
Shut up!</b></Default>

c0000358
00:16:15.980 --> 00:16:18.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're only here at all because
you care about my big sister!</b></Default>

c0000359
00:16:18.690 --> 00:16:20.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's right! Because
if something happened to you,</b></Default>

c0000360
00:16:20.560 --> 00:16:22.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it would make Mai sad!
- That isn't true!</b></Default>

c0000361
00:16:22.610 --> 00:16:23.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, it is!</b></Default>

c0000362
00:16:23.980 --> 00:16:25.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's not a doubt in my mind</b></Default>

c0000363
00:16:25.320 --> 00:16:26.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she'd be heartbroken over you!</b></Default>

c0000364
00:16:26.820 --> 00:16:28.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She said she hated me
to my face!</b></Default>

c0000365
00:16:28.950 --> 00:16:30.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And that was the lie!
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000366
00:16:33.620 --> 00:16:35.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where's the proof?</b></Default>

c0000367
00:16:36.660 --> 00:16:38.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Fine, then.
I'm gonna show you.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:16:43.590 --> 00:16:45.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You shouldn't be doin' that.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:16:45.250 --> 00:16:47.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Swimming's prohibited in
this area, you know.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:16:53.510 --> 00:16:54.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-
What is this?</b></Default>

c0000371
00:16:54.850 --> 00:16:56.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You'll see when you open it.
- Annoying.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:17:00.690 --> 00:17:01.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000373
00:17:02.440 --> 00:17:04.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These are all letters I wrote.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:17:05.400 --> 00:17:06.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

c0000375
00:17:06.940 --> 00:17:07.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't get it.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:17:08.690 --> 00:17:09.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I...</b></Default>

c0000377
00:17:09.740 --> 00:17:11.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How come?</b></Default>

c0000378
00:17:11.360 --> 00:17:13.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Because she was happy
to receive them, obviously.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:17:14.910 --> 00:17:16.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She treasured all the letters
that you sent.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:17:17.870 --> 00:17:20.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would someone who hates you
go through the trouble</b></Default>

c0000381
00:17:20.330 --> 00:17:21.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to do this?
- But I'm not even...</b></Default>

c0000382
00:17:22.750 --> 00:17:23.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000383
00:17:23.790 --> 00:17:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A real little sister.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:17:25.840 --> 00:17:26.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you even mean?</b></Default>

c0000385
00:17:29.340 --> 00:17:31.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Back when I wrote these,</b></Default>

c0000386
00:17:31.220 --> 00:17:33.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't know that my big sister
and I had different mothers</b></Default>

c0000387
00:17:33.930 --> 00:17:36.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and what it meant
for our situation.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:17:36.220 --> 00:17:37.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And when I figured it out,</b></Default>

c0000389
00:17:37.470 --> 00:17:39.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I felt anxious about it all
the time.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:17:39.640 --> 00:17:41.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I figured that I must have
been nothing but a nuisance</b></Default>

c0000391
00:17:42.020 --> 00:17:43.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to her all along.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:17:43.730 --> 00:17:45.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I couldn't write
those letters anymore!</b></Default>

c0000393
00:17:47.190 --> 00:17:48.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So that's what she thinks.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:17:48.820 --> 00:17:50.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But what do you think of it,
Mai?</b></Default>

c0000395
00:17:50.490 --> 00:17:51.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000396
00:17:54.030 --> 00:17:56.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't look through people's
treasures without asking first.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:17:57.410 --> 00:17:58.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But why?</b></Default>

c0000398
00:18:00.580 --> 00:18:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big sis.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:18:02.790 --> 00:18:05.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Back then all I remember
is that I had so much on</b></Default>

c0000400
00:18:05.670 --> 00:18:07.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my plate,
it made me dizzy.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:18:07.800 --> 00:18:09.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I did after getting home
was sleep.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:18:10.260 --> 00:18:13.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't even have time to watch
the shows I was appearing in.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:18:14.050 --> 00:18:17.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sure, I got complimented all
the time but all I could think</b></Default>

c0000404
00:18:17.510 --> 00:18:19.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was, "Who are these people?"</b></Default>

c0000405
00:18:21.140 --> 00:18:23.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were completely different,
though, Nodoka.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:18:24.020 --> 00:18:25.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you were introduced
as my kid sister,</b></Default>

c0000407
00:18:26.020 --> 00:18:28.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had no idea how to feel.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:18:28.110 --> 00:18:30.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But then you'd send
these letters to me,</b></Default>

c0000409
00:18:30.440 --> 00:18:33.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>telling me, "Good job,"
or just saying that I'm awesome.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:18:34.280 --> 00:18:36.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And each one gave me courage.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:18:36.620 --> 00:18:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I felt as long
as it would make you happy,</b></Default>

c0000412
00:18:38.950 --> 00:18:40.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I could keep working hard.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:18:40.870 --> 00:18:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And because of that,</b></Default>

c0000414
00:18:42.080 --> 00:18:44.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came to truly
like doing my job.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:18:44.830 --> 00:18:47.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So Nodoka,
thanks for that.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:18:47.540 --> 00:18:48.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000417
00:18:49.170 --> 00:18:51.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And for being
my little sister.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:18:51.420 --> 00:18:52.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thank you.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:18:53.010 --> 00:18:55.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000420
00:18:55.260 --> 00:18:56.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, big sis, I...</b></Default>

c0000421
00:18:57.800 --> 00:18:59.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, you're not being fair!</b></Default>

c0000422
00:18:59.850 --> 00:19:01.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The damage
has already been done.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:19:01.350 --> 00:19:03.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's too late!
[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000424
00:19:04.020 --> 00:19:06.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was really trying
to do my best.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:19:06.850 --> 00:19:08.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But why do you get to be
the lead vocal on</b></Default>

c0000426
00:19:08.560 --> 00:19:10.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a song before me?</b></Default>

c0000427
00:19:10.320 --> 00:19:13.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And why do you get to be praised
by my mother before me?</b></Default>

c0000428
00:19:13.400 --> 00:19:15.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Because I put the practice in.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:19:15.280 --> 00:19:17.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I kept practicing
every single day.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:19:17.410 --> 00:19:19.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's what I'm talking about!</b></Default>

c0000431
00:19:19.160 --> 00:19:21.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter how hard something is,
you do what you need to do,</b></Default>

c0000432
00:19:21.910 --> 00:19:23.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and if you can't do it,
you take full ownership!</b></Default>

c0000433
00:19:23.910 --> 00:19:25.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're awesome like that
and I hate it!</b></Default>

c0000434
00:19:26.250 --> 00:19:27.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000435
00:19:27.210 --> 00:19:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groaning]</b></Default>

c0000436
00:19:29.090 --> 00:19:30.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That hurt!
Why'd you hit me?</b></Default>

c0000437
00:19:31.050 --> 00:19:32.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:19:32.420 --> 00:19:34.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't take how much
of a brat she was being.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:19:34.130 --> 00:19:35.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My anger flared up.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:19:35.170 --> 00:19:36.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm pretty sure you hit</b></Default>

c0000441
00:19:36.180 --> 00:19:37.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the wrong person, though.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:19:37.640 --> 00:19:39.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She has a magazine
shoot tomorrow, right?</b></Default>

c0000443
00:19:39.890 --> 00:19:41.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What'll she do if I leave
a mark?</b></Default>

c0000444
00:19:42.180 --> 00:19:44.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's stuff like that, too.
[both grunting]</b></Default>

c0000445
00:19:44.600 --> 00:19:46.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your level of professionalism
is just way too high!</b></Default>

c0000446
00:19:46.810 --> 00:19:48.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't even compete!</b></Default>

c0000447
00:19:48.940 --> 00:19:51.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's impossible for me.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:19:56.360 --> 00:19:57.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nodoka.</b></Default>

c0000449
00:19:58.780 --> 00:20:00.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When the concert ended,</b></Default>

c0000450
00:20:00.450 --> 00:20:03.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you saw your mother in line
for high fives, right?</b></Default>

c0000451
00:20:03.700 --> 00:20:05.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When it was her turn,</b></Default>

c0000452
00:20:05.080 --> 00:20:07.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she held my hand and I noticed
it was trembling.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:20:09.580 --> 00:20:11.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think she was feeling
really anxious until now.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:20:11.840 --> 00:20:13.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Anxious?</b></Default>

c0000455
00:20:13.460 --> 00:20:15.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-
She's been watching you
do everything you can</b></Default>

c0000456
00:20:15.460 --> 00:20:17.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to meet the expectations
she set.</b></Default>

c0000457
00:20:17.930 --> 00:20:19.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So she was worried about whether
or not you</b></Default>

c0000458
00:20:19.680 --> 00:20:22.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were actually happy all along.</b></Default>

c0000459
00:20:22.100 --> 00:20:24.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But she's never said that
to me.</b></Default>

c0000460
00:20:24.310 --> 00:20:25.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't understand.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:20:25.680 --> 00:20:28.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I mean, no matter
how anxious they are,</b></Default>

c0000462
00:20:28.270 --> 00:20:30.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a parent could never share
that with their kid.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:20:31.020 --> 00:20:32.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But I just...</b></Default>

c0000464
00:20:33.270 --> 00:20:35.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted...</b></Default>

c0000465
00:20:35.360 --> 00:20:37.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My mother was always mad
and all I wanted</b></Default>

c0000466
00:20:37.360 --> 00:20:39.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was for her to just be happy!</b></Default>

c0000467
00:20:39.280 --> 00:20:41.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She always talked about
how great you were</b></Default>

c0000468
00:20:41.120 --> 00:20:43.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I wanted her to give me
the same grace for once!</b></Default>

c0000469
00:20:43.490 --> 00:20:45.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just wanted my mother
to smile at me!</b></Default>

c0000470
00:20:46.790 --> 00:20:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
- Nodoka. From now on,</b></Default>

c0000471
00:20:49.790 --> 00:20:52.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>make her happy with something
you choose for yourself.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:20:52.670 --> 00:20:54.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not just the things she
tells you you should do.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:20:57.130 --> 00:20:58.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm-hmm.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:20:58.380 --> 00:20:59.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000475
00:20:59.340 --> 00:21:00.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000476
00:21:00.840 --> 00:21:03.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000477
00:21:03.800 --> 00:21:06.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry!
I'm so sorry, Mom!</b></Default>

c0000478
00:21:06.680 --> 00:21:08.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't mean to!</b></Default>

c0000479
00:21:20.320 --> 00:21:21.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, big sis?</b></Default>

c0000480
00:21:21.990 --> 00:21:23.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes?</b></Default>

c0000481
00:21:23.660 --> 00:21:27.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't--I don't have to be
exactly like you, do I?</b></Default>

c0000482
00:21:27.580 --> 00:21:30.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, but you can be
if you really want to be.</b></Default>

c0000483
00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:32.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't.</b></Default>

c0000484
00:21:33.290 --> 00:21:34.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000485
00:21:36.670 --> 00:21:37.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

c0000486
00:21:38.300 --> 00:21:39.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000487
00:21:39.340 --> 00:21:41.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000488
00:21:41.430 --> 00:21:44.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, what just--
- We went back?</b></Default>

c0000489
00:21:44.180 --> 00:21:45.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000490
00:21:45.970 --> 00:21:47.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did we?</b></Default>

c0000491
00:21:47.310 --> 00:21:50.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We did it!
Sis, we're really back!</b></Default>

c0000492
00:21:50.140 --> 00:21:52.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nodoka, I'm so glad!</b></Default>

c0000493
00:21:52.600 --> 00:21:54.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [stammers]
[both laughing]</b></Default>

c0000494
00:21:54.610 --> 00:21:56.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000495
00:21:56.730 --> 00:21:59.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This means I can finally flirt
with my girlfriend again.</b></Default>

c0000496
00:21:59.940 --> 00:22:06.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big sis!
- Aww, don't cry.</b></Default>

c0000497
00:22:06.780 --> 00:22:09.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In the end I wonder
what triggered all of it.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:22:10.160 --> 00:22:11.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Starting from the beginning
it wasn't</b></Default>

c0000499
00:22:11.750 --> 00:22:13.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that their personas swapped,
right?</b></Default>

c0000500
00:22:13.210 --> 00:22:15.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, I guess so.</b></Default>

c0000501
00:22:15.080 --> 00:22:17.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was more like only
their appearances changed.</b></Default>

c0000502
00:22:17.380 --> 00:22:19.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The little sister's
subconscious thoughts--</b></Default>

c0000503
00:22:19.670 --> 00:22:22.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that she wants to be or has
to be like her big sister--</b></Default>

c0000504
00:22:22.590 --> 00:22:24.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are likely what transformed
her outward appearance</b></Default>

c0000505
00:22:24.680 --> 00:22:26.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into that of Mai Sakurajima.</b></Default>

c0000506
00:22:26.260 --> 00:22:27.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Probably, yeah.</b></Default>

c0000507
00:22:27.850 --> 00:22:29.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how do you explain that?</b></Default>

c0000508
00:22:29.560 --> 00:22:31.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you're asking about
the principle,</b></Default>

c0000509
00:22:31.390 --> 00:22:32.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's probably fair to assume
it's a type</b></Default>

c0000510
00:22:32.980 --> 00:22:34.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of quantum teleportation.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:22:35.150 --> 00:22:38.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah. Gorillas
are exceptionally smart, yeah?</b></Default>

c0000512
00:22:38.150 --> 00:22:39.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In other words,</b></Default>

c0000513
00:22:39.610 --> 00:22:41.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakurajima's little sister took
the blueprints</b></Default>

c0000514
00:22:41.740 --> 00:22:43.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for her big sister's
physical body</b></Default>

c0000515
00:22:43.200 --> 00:22:44.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and applied it to herself,</b></Default>

c0000516
00:22:44.570 --> 00:22:47.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and by observing it she was able
to assume</b></Default>

c0000517
00:22:47.450 --> 00:22:50.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and be perceived in
the physical role of her sister.</b></Default>

c0000518
00:22:50.200 --> 00:22:53.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then why did Mai look like
Toyohama as well?</b></Default>

c0000519
00:22:53.540 --> 00:22:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Could be the feeling
was mutual.</b></Default>

c0000520
00:22:55.540 --> 00:22:57.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you ever considered
the possibility</b></Default>

c0000521
00:22:57.250 --> 00:22:59.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that Sakurajima might also be
the slightest bit jealous</b></Default>

c0000522
00:22:59.670 --> 00:23:01.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of her little sister?</b></Default>

c0000523
00:23:01.130 --> 00:23:04.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000524
00:23:04.170 --> 00:23:07.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>["Fukashigi no Carte" plays]</b></Default>

c0000525
00:23:07.090 --> 00:23:14.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000526
00:23:40.130 --> 00:23:41.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000527
00:23:42.250 --> 00:23:43.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000528
00:23:43.880 --> 00:23:45.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell rings]</b></Default>

c0000529
00:23:45.550 --> 00:23:47.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The door's unlocked.
Come in.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:23:47.300 --> 00:23:50.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I'll let myself in now.
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000531
00:23:50.260 --> 00:23:52.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you here, Toyohama?</b></Default>

c0000532
00:23:52.180 --> 00:23:54.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Because as of today
I'll be living here.</b></Default>

c0000533
00:23:54.310 --> 00:23:55.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I thought you just fixed
the problems you</b></Default>

c0000534
00:23:55.810 --> 00:23:56.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>had with your mom.</b></Default>

c0000535
00:23:57.020 --> 00:23:58.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We had another fight
after that.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:23:58.730 --> 00:24:00.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Being told what
to do constantly's</b></Default>

c0000537
00:24:00.190 --> 00:24:01.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the worst, you know?</b></Default>

c0000538
00:24:01.270 --> 00:24:02.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you mean, you know?</b></Default>

c0000539
00:24:02.570 --> 00:24:04.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you're okay with this, Mai?</b></Default>

c0000540
00:24:04.610 --> 00:24:07.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, sorry.
Got a call from my agency.</b></Default>

c0000541
00:24:07.360 --> 00:24:09.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hi. Thanks for your hard work.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:24:09.700 --> 00:24:12.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I explained it to big sis
and she asked me</b></Default>

c0000543
00:24:12.370 --> 00:24:14.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I wanted to stay at her place
for a little while.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:24:15.080 --> 00:24:18.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And also, thank you.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000545
00:24:18.210 --> 00:24:21.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big sis said I should give you
a proper thanks.</b></Default>

c0000546
00:24:21.210 --> 00:24:24.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I made a whole lot of trouble
for you and you saved me.</b></Default>

c0000547
00:24:24.670 --> 00:24:26.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nah, it's fine.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:24:26.260 --> 00:24:28.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For me it was about getting
to flirt with Mai again</b></Default>

c0000549
00:24:28.970 --> 00:24:29.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as soon as possible.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:24:31.140 --> 00:24:32.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [laughing]</b></Default>

c0000551
00:24:32.680 --> 00:24:34.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I might understand it a
tiny bit now.</b></Default>

c0000552
00:24:34.640 --> 00:24:36.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?
- Why my sister might end up</b></Default>

c0000553
00:24:36.480 --> 00:24:37.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>choosing someone like you.</b></Default>

c0000554
00:24:37.980 --> 00:24:39.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000555
00:24:40.060 --> 00:24:42.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> - I'm terribly sorry about tha.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000556
00:24:42.440 --> 00:24:44.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes, I realize I'm
making trouble for you.</b></Default>

c0000557
00:24:44.270 --> 00:24:45.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.
- Mm?</b></Default>

c0000558
00:24:46.320 --> 00:24:47.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is something the matter?</b></Default>

c0000559
00:24:47.950 --> 00:24:49.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think we have a new problem
on our hands.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:24:55.790 --> 00:25:00.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, Sakuta.
You're such a rascal.</b></Default>

